Information


Office hours and working from home


Office hours: mostly between 8-16 CET but the office is always open if you have an access card


Calling in sick


Depends on terms of employment; PhD etc. email your supervisor and xxxx (the one who register sickness???). Post doc etc. in SDCA – email Niels Jessen (niels.jessen@biomed.au.dk) and Maria Siggaard marsig@rm.dk for registration


Holiday, days off, “first day with sick child” and “omsorgsdage”


Depends on terms of employment; PhD etc. email your supervisor and xxxx (the one who register holidays, sick child etc). Post doc etc. in SDCA – email Maria Siggaard marsig@rm.dk for registration


Salary


Contract. If question talk to Maria Siggaard, marsig@rm.dk


Maternity/paternity leave and other leaves


Ask Maria Siggaard, marsig@rm.dk


Funding applications

